# CubicEngine player model — Steve proportions
# 0.6m wide (X), 1.8m tall (Y), 0.3m deep (Z)
# Origin at center-bottom (feet)
# Units: metres (VOXEL_SIZE = 0.5m per voxel)
# Front face faces -Z (matches engine forward direction at yaw=0)

